 160:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****  *  the default/idle state) -> opto off -> R19 pulls G1 back down -> MOSFET
 161:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****  *  off -> SPS30 unpowered. Confirmed against the schematic, not assumed. */
